                <h2 data-uuid="9e729cb316974a44a3712787110e84fa"> Essential Question–Writing</h2>
                <p class="white" data-uuid="8c5c11ad9ef9449c90b186809d5495a8">In
                    this module you’ve learned about the growth of the United States before the
                    Civil War.
                    Now it’s your turn to demonstrate your understanding of the module content by
                    writing an essay.</p>
            </div>
            <h3 data-uuid="f7125d71fc884ca4a18d8a9ee9a94cd5">What historical forces were most important in shaping the United States before 1860?</h3>
            <p data-uuid="0bd46d43c46c4b02b08dcddc45ae6424">Write
                a persuasive essay answering this question. In your essay, discuss the
                democratic ideals that inspired American independence and our nation’s founding
                documents. Also, consider the nation’s growth, the factors that united the
                nation and divided it, as well as the experiences of its people. Be sure to cite
                evidence to support your position, and organize your essay into an
                introduction, body, and conclusion.</p>
        </section>
